text:
It is not required

As explained here:

https://github.com/vstakhov/libucl/#general-syntax-sugar

key = value;
section {
    key = value;
}

is equivalent to

{
    "key": "value",
    "section": {
        "key": "value"
    }
}


However, it would likely be stylistically better to be consistent throughout the file.
